{"tid":2341202,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《全民造星》十強拉票 K LAU：我主張唱多啲廣東話歌","createTime":"2020-12-26T06:58:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T11:48:19.000Z","uid":63183,"like":21,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"465539706c3526fbcc2b7659d6e46b3984771e48","tid":2341202,"uid":63183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T06:58:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/4876\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Farticles%2F4876&d=gNEzxY0d91fOO8mfTbt%2FUgmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=43b0f4be\" target=\"_blank\">https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/4876</a><br />\n《全民造星》十強拉票 K LAU：我主張唱多啲廣東話歌<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/gongjyuhok.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/KLAU.png?w=1200&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2FKLAU.png%3Fw%3D1200%26ssl%3D1&h=d8f0fc62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全民造星III喺今晚將會係十強嘅決賽，喺之前預賽、50強、20強都有好多參賽者演唱各種語言嘅歌曲，廣東話歌唔算太多。K LAU今年係第二次參賽，佢個人喺音樂有唔少提升嘅同事，亦改以廣東話RAP做主打。昨日接受報章訪問嘅時候，更加直言自己主張唱多啲廣東話歌，希望大家投佢一票。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/gongjyuhok.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/K-LAU.png?w=667&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2FK-LAU.png%3Fw%3D667%26ssl%3D1&h=254955c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢喺受訪影片到話：「ＨＥＬＬＯ大家好係我全民造星ＩＩＩ十強參賽者Ｋ ＬＡＵ。今年嘅我開始慢慢搵到自己嘅方向同喜愛嘅事，我都依然會喜愛跳唱，依然好鍾意見到喺台上好有火好有正能量嘅我自己。如果你哋之前我都希望你喺決賽入面投我一票，因為我都算係喺十強參賽者入面，其中一個我會係主張唱多啲廣東話歌啦，同埋我係會想喺每一隻上台嘅作品入邊，就算佢係唔係原創都好，我都想加我自己內心嘅想法去話畀你哋知Ｋ ＬＡＵ係一個乜嘢嘅歌手或者表演者。如果你都感受到我呢張熱誠嘅話，希望你哋可以26嘅總決賽入邊投我一票。」<br />\n<br />\n另外，參賽者Mischa同陳葦璇早前都透露會唱廣東話歌。葦璇會決定挑戰Solo唱慢歌，展現同跳唱唔同嘅一面。Mischa就話：「今次決賽其中一首廣東話歌會唱自己嘅故事，因為很多時唱英文歌，好少唱廣東話，希望同觀眾連繫多一啲。」"},{"pid":"3076643b6357e61b0283a7bc1a256b0e98080d36","tid":2341202,"uid":138689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:04:12.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"e7a0ac69e73ea4c5c8db3c6fbac2ad1c20969beb","tid":2341202,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:14:38.000Z","msg":"好樣衰"},{"pid":"d97bd4ed866df7ccc881897f68b82a0b2da042ea","tid":2341202,"uid":59852,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:16:49.000Z","msg":"基爾獸"},{"pid":"850038e8c3fde2467d553dd543d9076d7116c417","tid":2341202,"uid":335664,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:19:19.000Z","msg":"猿人？"},{"pid":"82eebb54b17f02bdc5af66733be73d6cf7efdb60","tid":2341202,"uid":162406,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:39:28.000Z","msg":"唔撐自己人都已經冇咩所謂 仲要踩多兩腳 黃圈俾自己人鬥死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc467a98618df6276a60d315acd13b6019f0c388","tid":2341202,"uid":122672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:49:20.000Z","msg":"黃圈星星王"},{"pid":"24c6721f0bddf158b13600685a0cd86c57eaafa2","tid":2341202,"uid":44349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T08:34:52.000Z","msg":"有冇人投klau<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好欣賞佢創作粵語歌同黃"},{"pid":"6abb7b5e789d269c6eaa636f54a4228c5c198b52","tid":2341202,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82eebb54b17f02bdc5af66733be73d6cf7efdb60","tid":2341202,"uid":162406,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T07:39:28.000Z","msg":"唔撐自己人都已經冇咩所謂 仲要踩多兩腳 黃圈俾自己人鬥死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T11:44:12.000Z","msg":"真 唱廣東歌比賽已經好難得"},{"pid":"7586c98ae208b02a5d9fa1506c601613abc0fbe6","tid":2341202,"uid":260113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T11:48:19.000Z","msg":"支持廣東話歌<br />\n戴左口罩幾靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}